Hi all,
Ive playing around with UI Extensions and serveless functions.
Ive got my code to run locally but when i move the code into a serverless function for the extensions i start getting an error: "AxiosError: connect ETIMEDOUT".

is this a timeout error from HubSpot because the serverless function is taking too long to run?

Much appreciated
what is your vote on most cost-effective platform for hosting a webhook url, and hosting your function to post or patch the info to HubSpot?
